        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【🍎#这两个时间段不宜吃苹果#】不管是早上吃、中午吃还是晚上吃，苹果的营养价值都没有改变。#什么时间吃苹果更合适#？①早上吃可以帮助恢复精力，促进肠道蠕...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【🍎<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E6%AE%B5%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E5%90%83%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E6%AE%B5%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E5%90%83%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#这两个时间段不宜吃苹果#</span></a>】不管是早上吃、中午吃还是晚上吃，苹果的营养价值都没有改变。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%90%83%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%9B%B4%E5%90%88%E9%80%82%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%90%83%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%9B%B4%E5%90%88%E9%80%82%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#什么时间吃苹果更合适#</span></a>？①早上吃可以帮助恢复精力，促进肠道蠕动，改善排便。②饭前吃增加饱腹感，利于减肥。不过，胃酸过多的人，不建议早上空腹吃苹果。需要注意的是，苹果不宜饭后立即吃，也不宜睡前吃<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[馋嘴]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chanzui-fc1acc341b.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6j3NaPo" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
